'''Contract-Scribe''' was a title used in the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]]. Contract-Scribes were aides who accompanied the [[Viceroy of the Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation Viceroy]] to important meetings, and perused documents to ensure that the Viceroy's goals were met.

